# dotnet build artifacts. The root .gitignore's Unity-oriented /[Oo]bj/ and
# /[Bb]uild/ patterns are anchored to the repo root, so they don't reach
# nested bin/obj dirs here -- this package needs its own. Outputs are
# redirected to bin~/obj~ (Directory.Build.props) so Unity's importer --
# which skips ~-suffixed folders -- never sees dotnet-built dlls; the
# plain names stay listed as a belt-and-suspenders for anyone building
# with older tooling that ignores the props file.
bin/
obj/
bin~/
obj~/

# The root .gitignore blanket-ignores *.csproj (Unity's auto-generated IDE
# project files under Assets/). Nothing under this package is Unity --
# these ARE the hand-authored source defining the package, not generated
# cruft -- so un-ignore them.
!*.csproj
